name: Suspicious Nanas Cake
desc: A cake with a fascinating shape. It was a little deformed when you took it out of the pot, and its texture is a bit too soft. You can't help but think back on the cooking process... and how the cake tastes like it's just been dredged up from the sea.

value.text: Increases all party members' ATK by 160 for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
